<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Abortive1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Abortive,</orth> adj. 1) born before the due time: <cit><quote>why should I joy in any a. birth?</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.104" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 104</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) monstrous, unnatural: <cit><quote>allay this thy a. pride,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 60</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if ever he have child, a. be it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 21</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.228" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 228</bibl>.
